Reign Over Me is a 2007 American drama film written and directed by Mike Binder , and produced by his brother Jack Binder .
The film stars Adam Sandler , Don Cheadle , Jada Pinkett Smith , Liv Tyler , Donald Sutherland , Saffron Burrows and Mike Binder himself .
Distributed by Columbia Pictures , the film was released on March 23 , 2007 .
The film was released to DVD , and Blu-ray on October 9 , 2007 .